<br>
The (probably baseless) worry was that visible damage would reveal how little we actually contribute to a group like that, and we would get disbanded on that basis.<br>
<br>
Of course, this little secret managed to get around anyway...resulting in our large upgrade in Luclin.  I think it is too soon to say, but my take from reading this board is that we are in good shape.  Enough whining is present to show that we aren't overpowered (and due for a smack with the nerf bat), but that we are holding our own again.  It would be cool if other classes got to see our occational critical hit though, in the same way they see a warrior's (and with luclin, all melee classes)<br>
<br>
Whoever was in charge at the time posted something to the effect that he saw how split wizards were on the subject, and he wasn't going to throw any resources at changing something to make the happy half pissed off, even if it made the unhappy half pleased.<br>
<br>
